295
00:20:14,138 --> 00:20:15,219
be used by others

296
00:20:15,858 --> 00:20:17,899
and then discarded like trash.

297
00:20:18,499 --> 00:20:19,578
I never imagined

298
00:20:21,298 --> 00:20:23,058
that a shrewd man

299
00:20:23,179 --> 00:20:25,058
like you could also

300
00:20:26,219 --> 00:20:28,298
experience unrequited desires.

301
00:20:31,019 --> 00:20:31,859
Miss Xu,

302
00:20:32,459 --> 00:20:34,019
if you continue this outburst,

303
00:20:34,298 --> 00:20:35,778
