312
00:21:00,578 --> 00:21:01,499
You tell me to return.

313
00:21:02,179 --> 00:21:04,378
Tell me where I should go.

314
00:21:05,098 --> 00:21:06,659
Where should I go? Tell me.

315
00:21:06,659 --> 00:21:07,499
Tell me!

316
00:21:11,058 --> 00:21:11,898
Miss Xu.

317
00:21:14,578 --> 00:21:15,418
What?

318
00:21:16,298 --> 00:21:17,858
You think yourself the greatest victim?

319
00:21:18,778 --> 00:21:21,058
What of those sold into slavery
and forced to grovel?

320
00:21:21,059 --> 00:21:23,298
Or those displaced
and begging on the streets?

321
00:21:23,939 --> 00:21:25,138
Your father's death

322
00:21:26,259 --> 00:21:27,858
was nothing but his deserved punishment.

323
00:21:28,338 --> 00:21:31,058
You still live in luxury.

324
00:21:31,378 --> 00:21:33,739
Only deprived of your former status.

325
00:21:36,058 --> 00:21:37,058
And you're whining now?

326
00:21:41,818 --> 00:21:42,778
You deceived me,

327
00:21:43,618 --> 00:21:44,458
betrayed me,

328
00:21:45,019 --> 00:21:45,859
and dumped me.

329
00:21:47,019 --> 00:21:48,419
But I'd let it all slide.

330
00:21:50,858 --> 00:21:53,058
How could you betray my father?

331
00:21:55,058 --> 00:21:57,578
He may have been a monster to the world,

332
00:21:58,499 --> 00:22:00,739
but he never did you any harm.

333
00:22:04,019 --> 00:22:05,098
In this situation,

334
00:22:05,979 --> 00:22:07,659
you still act superior.

335
00:22:09,979 --> 00:22:11,259
I don't know if this is pitiful

336
00:22:12,858 --> 00:22:13,939
or laughable.

337
00:22:18,459 --> 00:22:19,299
Chu Zhao.

338
00:22:46,538 --> 00:22:47,378
Yingxiang.

339
00:22:48,659 --> 00:22:49,499
Yingxiang.

340
00:22:51,778 --> 00:22:52,618
Ying...

341
00:22:53,179 --> 00:22:54,019
Yingxiang.

342
00:22:54,899 --> 00:22:55,739
Yingxiang.

343
00:22:58,978 --> 00:23:00,658
Guards!

344
00:23:00,899 --> 00:23:01,739
Guards!

345
00:23:02,298 --> 00:23:04,259
Go fetch a physician. Hurry!

346
00:23:04,259 --> 00:23:05,099
Yes.

347
00:23:06,818 --> 00:23:07,658
Yingxiang.

348
00:23:08,259 --> 00:23:09,099
It's okay, Yingxiang.

349
00:23:09,099 --> 00:23:11,219
It's okay. Don't worry, Yingxiang.

350
00:23:11,219 --> 00:23:12,059
You will be okay.

351
00:23:12,699 --> 00:23:13,539
I

352
00:23:14,459 --> 00:23:15,299
don't fear.

353
00:23:18,298 --> 00:23:19,338
I only fear

354
00:23:21,138 --> 00:23:22,019
in the world,

355
00:23:24,778 --> 00:23:26,699
you'll end up alone.

356
00:23:32,459 --> 00:23:33,459
From now on,

357
00:23:35,899 --> 00:23:37,219
stop pushing yourself so hard.

358
00:23:42,019 --> 00:23:42,859
Spare...

359
00:23:43,818 --> 00:23:45,419
Spare yourself.

360
00:23:57,618 --> 00:23:58,458
Chu Zilan.

361
00:23:59,259 --> 00:24:00,378
This is your karma.

362
00:24:01,019 --> 00:24:01,859
Those you love

363
00:24:01,899 --> 00:24:02,858
