364
00:24:03,378 --> 00:24:04,298
Those who love you

365
00:24:05,338 --> 00:24:06,899
abandon you.

366
00:24:07,312 --> 00:24:09,744
♪Yet I yearn to stand opposed to you♪

367
00:24:09,858 --> 00:24:11,019
This is your karma.

368
00:24:12,138 --> 00:24:12,978
Karma!

369
00:24:14,138 --> 00:24:15,778
This is your karma!

370
00:24:18,563 --> 00:24:21,296
♪Upon towering fortress walls♪

371
00:24:21,296 --> 00:24:24,081
♪Brooding over lamented pasts♪

372
00:24:24,081 --> 00:24:27,088
♪Where shall light be found♪

373
00:24:27,088 --> 00:24:29,168
♪Once♪

374
00:24:29,476 --> 00:24:31,856
♪I had an unbreakable faith♪

375
00:24:32,298 --> 00:24:33,179
Get out!

376
00:24:33,298 --> 00:24:34,138
Listen.

377
00:24:34,138 --> 00:24:35,459
No customers,

378
00:24:35,499 --> 00:24:36,339
no coming back today!

379
00:24:36,619 --> 00:24:38,338
Stop putting on airs like noble ladies!

380
00:24:38,378 --> 00:24:40,299
Did your father even accept you?

381
00:24:41,058 --> 00:24:42,098
I'll teach you a lesson!

382
00:24:42,659 --> 00:24:43,499
Stop!

383
00:24:43,984 --> 00:24:45,857
♪Heartache♪

384
00:24:45,857 --> 00:24:48,912
♪Resenting the lonely years♪

385
00:24:49,098 --> 00:24:49,938
Leave with me.

386
00:24:51,267 --> 00:24:53,392
♪Not let it go♪

387
00:24:54,020 --> 00:24:58,436
♪Tears crystallize to frost♪

388
00:24:59,524 --> 00:25:02,192
♪Clutching stubborn obsessions♪

389
00:25:02,192 --> 00:25:05,673
♪Yet falling into folly♪

390
00:25:05,956 --> 00:25:07,536
♪Fading into oblivion♪

391
00:25:07,536 --> 00:25:10,996
♪Yet memories surge everywhere♪

392
00:25:11,716 --> 00:25:14,128
♪After the separation♪

393
00:25:14,532 --> 00:25:20,792
♪My heart feels adrift♪

394
00:25:20,792 --> 00:25:23,747
(Virtues' Enduring Legacy)

395
00:25:23,747 --> 00:25:26,576
(Ancestral Tablets of the Xiao Clan)

396
00:25:51,338 --> 00:25:52,178
Huaijin,

397
00:25:52,818 --> 00:25:54,219
yesterday, you read the decree

398
00:25:54,858 --> 00:25:56,259
not just under imperial pressure,

399
00:25:56,979 --> 00:25:58,419
but also to shield me and my wife,

400
00:25:58,658 --> 00:25:59,818
and to protect the Xiao Army.

401
00:26:00,939 --> 00:26:02,378
Since childhood, you've shouldered

402
00:26:02,899 --> 00:26:04,739
too much for our family

403
00:26:05,699 --> 00:26:06,618
and me.

404
00:26:07,538 --> 00:26:09,858
Always walking on thin ice
and bearing heavy burdens.

405
00:26:10,939 --> 00:26:12,459
But since Miss He arrived,

406
00:26:13,298 --> 00:26:14,378
you've been a lot brighter

407
00:26:15,338 --> 00:26:16,618
and more open.

408
00:26:18,219 --> 00:26:19,059
As your brother,

409
00:26:19,259 --> 00:26:20,699
I'm deeply grateful to Miss He.

410
00:26:26,098 --> 00:26:26,938
But Huaijin,

411
00:26:28,259 --> 00:26:29,939
you've already given too much.

412
00:26:30,899 --> 00:26:33,298
Don't sacrifice your marriage.

413
00:26:33,538 --> 00:26:36,059
This is unfair to both of you.

414
00:26:37,778 --> 00:26:38,899
Don't overthink it.

415
00:26:39,578 --> 00:26:40,578
No matter what,

416
00:26:40,979 --> 00:26:41,939
we will

417
00:26:42,298 --> 00:26:43,699
always support you.

418
00:26:50,699 --> 00:26:52,019
Why are you still here?

419
00:26:52,498 --> 00:26:53,338
Are you just going

420
00:26:53,338 --> 00:26:54,978
to wait until Miss He marries others?

421
00:26:55,259 --> 00:26:56,099
Can you bear that?

422
00:27:08,164 --> 00:27:11,696
(General Feihong's Mansion)

423
00:27:15,843 --> 00:27:17,577
♪Constant yearning♪

424
00:27:18,040 --> 00:27:21,803
♪Still vivid as our first meeting♪

425
00:27:23,031 --> 00:27:25,033
♪Endless gazing♪

426
00:27:25,609 --> 00:27:29,559
♪Step by step, falling deeper♪

427
00:27:29,559 --> 00:27:31,430
♪How to untangle this love♪

428
00:27:31,703 --> 00:27:37,196
♪Buried deep within dreams♪

429
00:27:38,377 --> 00:27:43,620
♪My heart, unyielding as stone,
remains true♪

430
00:27:44,699 --> 00:27:45,699
Why have you come?

431
00:27:47,618 --> 00:27:48,618
I can't let you go.

432
00:27:49,699 --> 00:27:50,539
I can't get past it.

433
00:27:55,179 --> 00:27:56,098
I can't give you up.

434
00:27:59,127 --> 00:28:03,561
♪Time lingers as you and I share
overlapping palm lines♪

435
00:28:03,561 --> 00:28:07,453
♪Zither and harp
accompany our dancing dreams♪

436
00:28:07,979 --> 00:28:09,058
Then why did you

437
00:28:10,459 --> 00:28:11,979
come to see me only now?

438
00:28:14,378 --> 00:28:15,378
Is it still possible?

439
00:28:22,211 --> 00:28:28,464
♪In the vast world,
I searched for years♪

440
00:28:29,668 --> 00:28:35,424
♪Shadows hustle. Scenes reappear♪

441
00:28:35,424 --> 00:28:38,224
♪What is there to fear♪

442
00:28:38,224 --> 00:28:43,986
♪We'll weather storms together♪

443
00:28:45,338 --> 00:28:46,459
Of course it's not too late.

444
00:28:48,298 --> 00:28:49,578
No one can force me to do

445
00:28:50,659 --> 00:28:51,739
what I refuse to do

446
00:28:53,098 --> 00:28:54,659
or marry whom I refuse to marry.

447
00:28:55,492 --> 00:28:58,598
♪Splendor fades from your eyes♪

448
00:28:58,659 --> 00:29:00,098
I'm done with overthinking

449
00:29:01,538 --> 00:29:02,618
and hesitation.

450
00:29:04,858 --> 00:29:05,698
Now,

451
00:29:07,378 --> 00:29:08,899
I'm doing what I want.

452
00:29:09,828 --> 00:29:12,939
♪Zither and harp
accompany our dancing dreams♪

453
00:29:12,939 --> 00:29:14,219
I understand your struggles.

454
00:29:15,419 --> 00:29:16,538
You care for me,

455
00:29:17,579 --> 00:29:19,739
but how can you abandon your army?

456
00:29:20,939 --> 00:29:22,098
I've convinced His Majesty.

457
00:29:23,338 --> 00:29:24,219
I won't marry you

458
00:29:25,419 --> 00:29:26,699
or anyone else.

459
00:29:28,499 --> 00:29:30,378
With or without a marriage contract,

460
00:29:32,778 --> 00:29:33,618
He Yan,

461
00:29:35,298 --> 00:29:37,098
you're my chosen wife.

462
00:29:40,419 --> 00:29:41,419
And I choose you too.

463
00:29:44,004 --> 00:29:50,080
♪The brocade moon writes our vow,
keeping this promise♪

464
00:30:07,459 --> 00:30:13,168
(Happiness, Groom's Procession)

465
00:30:28,939 --> 00:30:29,939
I keep thinking

466
00:30:30,339 --> 00:30:31,179
you're still

467
00:30:31,179 --> 00:30:32,419
that naive young girl.

468
00:30:32,899 --> 00:30:33,739
But now,

469
00:30:34,098 --> 00:30:34,979
you're a bride.

470
00:30:37,338 --> 00:30:38,178
Yan,

471
00:30:39,098 --> 00:30:40,499
I'm suddenly scared.

472
00:30:40,538 --> 00:30:41,378
What should I do?

473
00:30:42,818 --> 00:30:43,739
After today,

474
00:30:44,098 --> 00:30:45,378
you'll have a new identity.

475
00:30:45,939 --> 00:30:46,779
It's natural

476
00:30:46,979 --> 00:30:48,138
to feel nervous.

477
00:30:50,179 --> 00:30:51,019
But Taotao,

478
00:30:52,538 --> 00:30:53,378
remember.

479
00:30:54,138 --> 00:30:55,058
Whether you are

480
00:30:55,298 --> 00:30:56,338
someone's wife

481
00:30:56,659 --> 00:30:57,578
or a mother,

482
00:30:58,699 --> 00:30:59,618
never forget

483
00:31:00,259 --> 00:31:01,778
that above all, you are yourself.

484
00:31:03,818 --> 00:31:05,298
Don't let any single identity

485
00:31:05,659 --> 00:31:06,499
confine you.

486
00:31:12,858 --> 00:31:13,818
I won't forget.

487
00:31:15,739 --> 00:31:17,098
I have my aspirations to pursue

488
00:31:18,058 --> 00:31:19,098
and books I want to write.

489
00:31:20,138 --> 00:31:21,618
Whether Cheng Lisu is with me or not,

490
00:31:22,419 --> 00:31:23,378
I'll see them through.

491
00:31:26,259 --> 00:31:27,459
Why the sudden tears?

492
00:31:27,979 --> 00:31:29,818
