your makeup will smudge.

493
00:31:31,179 --> 00:31:32,659
It just occurred to me

494
00:31:33,818 --> 00:31:35,259
that if you wore bridal attire,

495
00:31:35,618 --> 00:31:37,019
you'd outshine everyone in Yaojing.

496
00:31:37,499 --> 00:31:38,778
Even more radiant than me.

497
00:31:40,019 --> 00:31:41,058
But now...

498
00:31:46,098 --> 00:31:48,099
Who cares about marriage?

499
00:31:48,939 --> 00:31:50,298
I'll still be a general,

500
00:31:50,659 --> 00:31:51,499
live my life,

501
00:31:51,858 --> 00:31:52,939
and enjoy my freedom.

502
00:31:53,979 --> 00:31:55,219
Alright, stop crying.

503
00:31:55,459 --> 00:31:57,818
Save those tears
for the wedding procession later.

504
00:32:05,939 --> 00:32:07,578
The bride alights from her sedan!

505
00:32:07,899 --> 00:32:10,058
Blessings descend!

506
00:32:11,699 --> 00:32:13,138
The couple enters the gate!

507
00:32:13,578 --> 00:32:15,618
Fortunes arrive!

508
00:32:26,378 --> 00:32:29,058
The star of fortune clears all paths!

509
00:32:29,459 --> 00:32:33,219
Step over the saddle for good omens!

510
00:32:39,019 --> 00:32:40,378
The bride crosses the saddle!

511
00:32:40,899 --> 00:32:42,979
May peace and wishes be granted!

512
00:32:44,538 --> 00:32:45,378
Come on.

513
00:32:52,659 --> 00:32:54,778
Step over the saddle!

514
00:33:05,978 --> 00:33:06,818
Cheng Lisu.

515
00:33:06,818 --> 00:33:07,658
Don't be angry.

516
00:33:07,658 --> 00:33:09,259
I just wanted to surprise you.

517
00:33:09,578 --> 00:33:10,418
See.

518
00:33:18,098 --> 00:33:19,939
Turning the felt like a scroll,

519
00:33:20,298 --> 00:33:23,058
joy yearns to be whole.

520
00:33:26,179 --> 00:33:27,419
Husband and wife turn the felt,

521
00:33:27,899 --> 00:33:29,618
may your house brim with descendants!

522
00:33:34,459 --> 00:33:36,298
Good fortune hides in the fans!

523
00:33:36,818 --> 00:33:39,578
Open them with a smile!

524
00:34:11,499 --> 00:34:12,858
Fans open!

525
00:34:13,339 --> 00:34:15,979
Flowers bloom with prosperity!

526
00:34:45,138 --> 00:34:47,138
First bow to heaven and earth!

527
00:34:55,258 --> 00:34:57,138
Second bow to the parents!

528
00:35:02,538 --> 00:35:04,299
Peace throughout the year!

529
00:35:10,058 --> 00:35:11,779
The couple bows to each other!

530
00:35:14,258 --> 00:35:16,058
A century of devotion!

531
00:35:17,379 --> 00:35:19,538
The ceremony is complete!

532
00:35:20,419 --> 00:35:21,618
- Congrats.
- Congrats.

533
00:35:22,459 --> 00:35:23,299
Congrats.

534
00:35:32,578 --> 00:35:34,218
Who told you to wear this?

535
00:35:36,058 --> 00:35:37,499
I think this pouch looks great.

536
00:35:39,499 --> 00:35:40,859
Just don't tell anyone

537
00:35:41,098 --> 00:35:42,258
that I embroidered it.

538
00:35:46,618 --> 00:35:47,458
Get up.

539
00:35:47,499 --> 00:35:48,339
Get up.

540
00:35:50,499 --> 00:35:51,859
Send the newlyweds

541
00:35:52,138 --> 00:35:53,899
to the bridal chamber!

542
00:35:56,419 --> 00:35:58,178
Having such a lively wedding

543
00:35:59,538 --> 00:36:00,378
is truly wonderful.

544
00:36:18,538 --> 00:36:19,379
Sorry.

545
00:36:22,698 --> 00:36:23,538
No.

546
00:36:24,419 --> 00:36:28,178
Many lovers in this world
never get together.

547
00:36:29,058 --> 00:36:30,218
At least, we, here and now,

548
00:36:30,899 --> 00:36:32,138
can hold hands.

549
00:36:32,979 --> 00:36:34,058
Even without marriage,

550
00:36:34,779 --> 00:36:36,258
we'll grow old together.

551
00:37:12,899 --> 00:37:13,899
Why aren't you eating?

552
00:37:14,339 --> 00:37:15,339
In this freezing weather,

553
00:37:15,459 --> 00:37:16,779
we should have lamb hotpot.

554
00:37:22,658 --> 00:37:23,819
General Feihong, eat a lot.

555
00:37:24,379 --> 00:37:25,219
Get stronger.

556
00:37:25,779 --> 00:37:26,619
Put on some weight.

557
00:37:27,738 --> 00:37:30,979
