makes women attractive.

558
00:37:31,419 --> 00:37:33,658
Why do you think differently?

559
00:37:33,899 --> 00:37:34,739
Others' opinions

560
00:37:35,258 --> 00:37:36,098
mean nothing to me.

561
00:37:36,698 --> 00:37:37,939
I only want you

562
00:37:38,178 --> 00:37:39,299
to be vigorous and healthy,

563
00:37:39,859 --> 00:37:42,379
so you can triumph on battlefields.

564
00:37:42,779 --> 00:37:44,578
That's what I like to hear.

565
00:37:45,059 --> 00:37:48,499
Here's to you, General Fengyun.

566
00:37:51,618 --> 00:37:52,459
General Feihong.

567
00:38:03,339 --> 00:38:04,179
