571
00:38:14,658 --> 00:38:15,538
Wutuo attacks Mingshui

572
00:38:15,618 --> 00:38:16,819
and Huayuan simultaneously.

573
00:38:20,779 --> 00:38:22,419
No time to waste. Go to the palace now.

574
00:38:22,827 --> 00:38:24,985
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

575
00:38:25,089 --> 00:38:29,009
♪Unveiling scars,
